                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristokleia fille de Menestratos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristokleia daughter of Menestratos.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Aristokleia figlia di Menestratos.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The situation of the tomb cannot and will probably never be traced, as modern construction has wholly changed the landscape.</p>
